    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei salvatoris Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/327">Gisolfus</persName> vir gloriosissimus
                        Dei previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, pro
                        amore omni[potentis Dei] quam et pro remedium salutis anime nostre, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs> domni <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/4146">Petri</persName>, <rs key="#Personal_rank"
                            >veneravili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">pontifex</rs> &lt;sic>, in <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3495">episcopio
                            Salernitano</orgName> in qua &lt;sic> ipse domnus preest, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Inflow #Inheritance #Confiscation #Purchase #Forced_purchase #Gift #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >omnes res quantum nostri palatiii &lt;sic> pertinentes</rs> est aut
                        nostro tempore pertinentes fuerit, <rs
                            key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs">sibe de mortuorum</rs> seu
                        undecumque, da <rs key="#Rivers">ribus</rs> qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4720">Transu</placeName> et usque <rs
                            key="#Rivers">aquam</rs> de <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4721"
                            >Cornia</placeName> et da ipsa Cornia usque <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >flubium</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/2369">Tuscianum</placeName> et de
                        super usque serris de montibus; simulque et concedimus in eodem episcopio
                        quantum quantoque nostri palatii pertinentes est aut fuerit ultra ipsum
                        Tuscianum, nominatibe in <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4722">Campu in Toru</placeName> et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4723"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Dossa</placeName>, et in <placeName ref="#places/4724"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Scabella</placeName>, in <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Beccasano</placeName>, et <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4726">Liciniano</placeName>. Ideo hec omnia et in omnibus
                        quantum infra ipse fines et extra ipse finis quomodocumque predicti palatii
                        pertinentes est aut fuerit, in ipsis nominatibus locis et intro ips[e] finis
                        transactibus et funditus cum aquis et omnia infra se habentibus in iamdictam
                        sanctam [ecc]lesiam concessimus. In ea ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc
                        nostrum roboreum preceptum ea que prelegitur pars ipsius episcopii et eius
                        rectores omni tempore ipso habendum dominandum possidendum et omnia ex inde
                        faciendum quod voluerit; et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, comitibus,
                        castaldeis vela quibuscumque agentibus habeatis ex inde aliquando aliqua
                        molestia vel contrarietate, set perpetuis temporibus securo nomine ipsam
                        sanctam ecclesiam eos habeat et possideat. Quod vero preceptum concessionis
                        ex iussione supradicte potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"
                            ref="#people/4147">Ricchardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities">Salernum</placeName> in sacro palatio, de anno
                        vicesimoquinto principatus supradicti magni principis, mense martius,
                        indictione prima.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
